{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"76c2a80a1c","title":"转发西南军区关于镇反工作报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2e92e95a7c","index":0,"year":1951,"month":2,"day":28,"articleId":"76c2a80a1c"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"bc3db516a2","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"76c2a80a1c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为转发中共西南军区委员会关于镇压反革命工作报告写的批语。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0facf885b2","type":"title","text":"转发西南军区关于镇反工作报告的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"76c2a80a1c"},{"id":"bc3db516a2","type":"paragraph","text":"华东军区，中南军区，西北军区，华北军区，东北军区，并告西南军区各负责同志及党委会：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"76c2a80a1c"},{"id":"0543b85e75","type":"paragraph","text":"下面是西南军区党委会二月十五日的报告，其中所述各项，值得十分注意。望你们自己及所属省军区，对于镇压反革命及管训旧军官两大问题，参考西南经验，作正确的处理。所谓肠从不问，是指被追参加而未作环事，或未作较大坏事者。至于助恶有据，即是从犯，应当判罪，如主犯判死刑，从犯至少判徒刑，有些罪大的从犯应判死刑，不在肠从不问之列。军队中混入反革命分子问题，必须引起充分注意，并着手审查清理，以其结果上报","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"76c2a80a1c"},{"id":"112261cfe6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"76c2a80a1c"},{"id":"6ed3d035cf","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"76c2a80a1c"}],"page":{"id":"d5d025519a","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"76c2a80a1c","start":145,"end":145}}}},"__N_SSG":true}